16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 3-102, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 3-102. A. The State Board of Education shall meet in
20 regular session once each month. Special meetings may be called by
21 the president or by a majority of the members of the Board.
22 B. Upon written request by at least two members of the Board,
23 any member of the Board shall be authorized to place an item on a
24 Board agenda. The item shall be placed on the agenda for the next
